Plain text:
I have your calendar open
I'd like to schedule an appointment
For what date?
March 1st
What time would you like to start?
2 PM
How much time do you want to block out?
1 hour 
What shall we call it?
Lunch appointment
Ok, so here is a summary for you: You have a lunch appointment on March 1st at 2 PM for 1 hour.

Plain text:
Hi Katharina. Let's create a meeting. What is it about?
Who is Beyonce
Beyoncé Giselle Knowles-Carter (born September 4, 1981) is an American singer, songwriter, actress, and dancer. Beyoncé has been noted for her boundary-pushing artistry and her vocal ability. Her success has made her a cultural icon and earned her the nickname "Queen Bey". 
Do you want to meet them?
Yes
On which day is it?
On Friday.
Will it take the whole day? 
No
What time is your meeting?
At 10
Do you want me to create a meeting with Beyonce on Friday at 10?
Yes

Plain text:
Eines Tages, Baby, werden wir alt sein, oh Baby, werden wir alt sein
und an all die Geschichten denken, die wir hätten erzählen können. 
Ich, ich bin der Meister der Streiche, wenn´s um Selbstbetrug geht.
Bin ein Kleinkind vom Feinsten, wenn ich vor Aufgaben steh´.
Bin ein entschleunigtes Teilchen.
Kann auf Keinsten was reißen.
Lass´ mich begeistern für Leichtsinn, wenn ein anderer ihn lebt.
